you have to educate yourself.

00:11:29.910 --> 00:11:35.430
And growing up in a
segregated school system,

00:11:35.430 --> 00:11:38.730
creating six medical
doctors, is really unheard of,

00:11:38.730 --> 00:11:40.850
especially two of them were women.

00:11:40.850 --> 00:11:43.780
So, that was something.

00:11:43.780 --> 00:11:50.340
I think that when he
went to UT, Galveston,

00:11:50.340 --> 00:11:54.240
that was really eye-opening
