00:12:07.070 --> 00:12:11.150
So, think about, he got into 1936.

00:12:11.150 --> 00:12:15.990
They only accepted one
Mexican a year, and it was him.

00:12:15.990 --> 00:12:19.720 position:56%
Pretty remarkable life, you know, he
had to have top grades to do that.

00:12:19.720 --> 00:12:25.170
But sadly, after that big
accomplishment, no school in Texas

00:12:25.170 --> 00:12:30.070
