00:13:20.370 --> 00:13:24.760
And I'm sure what happened with
his good looks and his, you know,

00:13:24.760 --> 00:13:28.720
tall stature that they asked him,
"Okay, how old are you, Hector?"

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:30.020
And he said, "Sixteen."

00:13:30.020 --> 00:13:31.850
Okay, they wrote it down,
