00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:46.380
so he lied about his age
by one year just to get in.

00:13:46.380 --> 00:13:49.430 position:56%
So, he was trying to escape poverty.

00:13:49.430 --> 00:13:52.840
He was, you know, trying to
prepare for the rest of his life.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:57.690
So, when he got called to active
military duty in 1940 after he,

00:13:57.690 --> 00:14:11.270
1942, he was already had
been a commissioned officer.

00:14:11.270 --> 00:14:17.640
So, when he got called to
active military duty in 1942,

00:14:17.640 --> 00:14:22.830
