00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:37.100
I mean, it was just one thing after
another, one thing, one thing.

00:14:37.100 --> 00:14:39.280
So, did he give up?

00:14:39.280 --> 00:14:40.780
No, he did not.

00:14:40.780 --> 00:14:42.080
He did not give up.

00:14:42.080 --> 00:14:50.320
He never gave up, and so he finally
