He did not become a US citizen until
November 7, 1946, after he got out.

00:16:40.900 --> 00:16:43.520 position:56%
We always wondered, Jim and I always
wondered why he married my mother

00:16:43.520 --> 00:16:45.900
in 1945 in June.

00:16:45.900 --> 00:16:49.800
My older sister was born there
in Italy, but they stayed there.

00:16:49.800 --> 00:16:53.620
They stayed there for a
year, and now we found

00:16:53.620 --> 00:16:56.440
out he wasn't even a citizen.

00:16:56.440 --> 00:16:58.360
So, I think he waited
until last minute to do it.

00:16:58.360 --> 00:16:59.830
You know, we don't really know why,

00:16:59.830 --> 00:17:04.940
