citizen of this country.

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:35.910
And I think this says
a lot for immigrants

00:17:35.910 --> 00:17:38.430
that are coming here
and want a better life.

00:17:38.430 --> 00:17:42.280
I think he's a role model for that.

00:17:42.280 --> 00:17:48.790
You know, he was just a great
physician, and I think that working

00:17:48.790 --> 00:17:53.400
with him for ten years taught me
so many things and how he took care

00:17:53.400 --> 00:17:57.720
