00:17:59.790 --> 00:18:04.900
He never said no, if you can't
pay me, you'll come back later.

00:18:04.900 --> 00:18:10.140
That never happened, and he
was just a great physician,

00:18:10.140 --> 00:18:13.320 position:56%
and he cared so much about every
single one of his patients that came

00:18:13.320 --> 00:18:18.590 position:56%
in and all the children that came
in that he was able to take care of,

00:18:18.590 --> 00:18:21.140
and that is just a part of my life

00:18:21.140 --> 00:18:26.150 position:56%
that at the time I did not
recognize how important it was going

00:18:26.150 --> 00:18:27.550
to be for me.

00:18:27.550 --> 00:18:31.690
Now that I'm in healthcare
and think about all the things

00:18:31.690 --> 00:18:35.330
