00:22:29.080 --> 00:22:30.380
So, he left.

00:22:30.380 --> 00:22:32.250
He said, "I wanted to, I want
to be here a little bit longer

00:22:32.250 --> 00:22:34.770
because my wife is
expecting her first baby."

00:22:34.770 --> 00:22:36.970
And they told him no.

00:22:36.970 --> 00:22:40.750
So, his parents went to see
my father in his office,

00:22:40.750 --> 00:22:44.200
