effort to contact whoever needed

00:22:56.820 --> 00:23:00.610
to be contacted to make
sure that young man was back

00:23:00.610 --> 00:23:02.070
in Corpus Christi with his family.

00:23:02.070 --> 00:23:07.220 position:56%
So, this is, this is what he did,
