00:25:05.870 --> 00:25:09.830
And this young soldier was
killed in World War II,

00:25:09.830 --> 00:25:13.810
and his remains came back
to Three Rivers three years

00:25:13.810 --> 00:25:16.040
after he was killed.

00:25:16.040 --> 00:25:22.540
He was a private, Private Felix
Longoria, and his poor widow went

00:25:22.540 --> 00:25:29.540 position:56%
to Three Rivers and wanted to wake
Felix's body in the one funeral home

00:25:29.540 --> 00:25:36.520 position:56%
