00:25:36.520 --> 00:25:37.860
"No.

00:25:37.860 --> 00:25:42.810
We do not wake Mexicans
in our all-white chapel."

00:25:42.810 --> 00:25:45.280
So, she was, of course, devastated.

00:25:45.280 --> 00:25:50.320
She was young, she was alone,
