00:28:26.290 --> 00:28:30.240
about Mexican Americans
like my father,

00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:34.420
and I think that this is a
good, this is a good start,

00:28:34.420 --> 00:28:37.550
"The Inspiring Life of
Texan Hector P. Garcia."

00:28:37.550 --> 00:28:44.610
And I'm very proud of my book,
