&gt;&gt; I'm going to let, I'm going

00:43:28.030 --> 00:43:31.070
to let my husband answer
that question, right.

00:43:31.070 --> 00:43:34.820
I'm going to let him answer for me.

00:43:34.820 --> 00:43:37.860
&gt;&gt; Jim Akers: Cecilia always,
she'll get so mad at me

00:43:37.860 --> 00:43:42.170
