everyone has heard the saying,

00:43:42.170 --> 00:43:45.030
"The apple doesn't fall
too far from the tree."

00:43:45.030 --> 00:43:49.610
Well, Dr. Hector was the
tree, and here's the apple.

00:43:49.610 --> 00:43:52.030
You know, her memory
is like Dr. Hector's.

00:43:52.030 --> 00:43:53.330
He never forgot anything.

00:43:53.330 --> 00:43:55.850
I mean, he just, you know, he
always remembered people's names,

00:43:55.850 --> 00:43:58.360
all this stuff, and
she's the same way.

00:43:58.360 --> 00:44:02.310 position:56%
I have to be very careful about what
I tell her for the last 40 years

00:44:02.310 --> 00:44:05.030
because she remembers everything.

00:44:05.030 --> 00:44:10.840
But you know, I think he had a
very big influence on her life,

00:44:10.840 --> 00:44:14.150
and their work ethics
are a lot alike.

00:44:14.150 --> 00:44:17.080
They don't know when
to stop and, you know,

00:44:17.080 --> 00:44:18.850
she doesn't know what rest is.

00:44:18.850 --> 00:44:21.490
It's, you know, seven
days a week and, you know,

00:44:21.490 --> 00:44:24.130
I'm going till I can't go
any further, and then figure

00:44:24.130 --> 00:44:26.410
out some way to keep going.

00:44:26.410 --> 00:44:28.180
But she's a product of her father.

00:44:28.180 --> 00:44:34.020
There's no doubt about that, and
it's a mostly good product, so.

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:35.320
&gt;&gt; Cecilia Garcia-Akers:
He said mostly.

00:44:35.320 --> 00:44:39.060 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Jim Akers: Mostly, probably more
good than, a lot more good than bad,

00:44:39.060 --> 00:44:43.600
but you know, it's a great, it's
great for her to be honored,

00:44:43.600 --> 00:44:48.530
to be able to do this and write
this story about her father.

00:44:48.530 --> 00:44:53.240
And you know, he was such an
influence on her life and a lot

00:44:53.240 --> 00:44:56.530
of other people's, but
she's really taken this

00:44:56.530 --> 00:45:01.950
and done a great job of
promoting his legacy.

00:45:01.950 --> 00:45:06.100
And this all got started by
a promise we made her mother

00:45:06.100 --> 00:45:10.680
that we would not let his legacy go
untold, so we tried to keep it up.

00:45:10.680 --> 00:45:11.980
Thank you.

00:45:11.980 --> 00:45:13.280
&gt;&gt; Cecilia Garcia-Akers: Thanks.

