00:47:44.820 --> 00:47:47.290
by the end of the year, he's
going to be on the Points

00:47:47.290 --> 00:47:51.720
of Light Monument, probably
by the end of this year.

00:47:51.720 --> 00:47:54.430
So, that's something else that
we're going to be working on,

00:47:54.430 --> 00:47:56.840
Points of Light Monument.

00:47:56.840 --> 00:48:00.000
But that's how we got started,
and it's a promise to momma,

00:48:00.000 --> 00:48:05.590
and I think we've done
a pretty good job.

