00:50:58.470 --> 00:51:03.970
they don't really recruit new
members from more recent wars.

00:51:03.970 --> 00:51:07.600
They kind of stick
with the old guard.

00:51:07.600 --> 00:51:13.060 position:56%
I don't see a whole lot of new
members signing up, which is a shame

00:51:13.060 --> 00:51:14.730
because they have different needs.

00:51:14.730 --> 00:51:18.270
You know, I have had many, many
